"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-27-its-gift-ill-never-forget-lady-gaga-relishes-performance-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  American pop star, Stefani Germanotta, aka Lady Gaga, has relished her iconic performance at the Paris Olympic Games opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999945332416972, \"rank\": 3.897879488437214e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stefani Germanotta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga thrilled attendees with an iconic French cabaret classic, 'Mon Truc en Plumes' by Zizi Jeanmaire, from the base of the Eiffel Tower on Friday.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.857401132389708e-28, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zizi Jeanmaire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement released via V, the singer recounted the efforts she and her team made to achieve the iconic performance.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also appreciated French people for the opportunity to perform at the Olympic Games, describing it as \\\"a gift\\\" she would never forget.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel so completely grateful to have been asked to open the Paris @Olympics 2024 this year.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999351985, \"rank\": 6.471411729419389e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also humbled to be asked by the Olympics organizing committee to sing such a special French song-a song to honor the French people and their tremendous history of art, music, and theatre.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This song was sung by Zizi Jeanmaire, born in Paris a French ballerina, she famously sang 'Mon Truc en Plumes' in 1961.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zizi Jeanmaire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\"}, {\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999351985, \"rank\": 6.471411729419389e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The title means 'My Thing with Feathers.'\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And this is not the first time we have crossed paths.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zizi starred in Cole Porter's musical 'Anything Goes' which was my first jazz release,\\\" the statement said partly.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Strallen\", \"score\": 0.9999999688957364, \"rank\": 2.0551534773945417e-08, \"text\": \"Zizi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Strallen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Strallen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga stated that although she is not French, she has \\\"always felt a very special connection with French people and singing French music.\\\"\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.857401132389708e-28, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We rented pom poms from Le Lido archive-a real French cabaret theater.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We collaborated with Dior to create custom costumes, using naturally molted feathers.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I studied French choreography that put a modern twist on a French classic.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\", \"score\": 0.9999999999943157, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French classic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I rehearsed tirelessly to study a joyful French dance, brushing up on some old skills-I bet you did not know I used to dance at a 60's French party on the lower east side when I was first starting out!\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.884992022154031, \"rank\": 0.12990035566805402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"score\": 0.999999999962256, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope you love this performance as much as I do.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And to everyone in France, thank you so much for welcoming me to your country to sing in honor of you-it's a gift I will never forget!\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996130025056671, \"rank\": 0.0003790520536317999, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congratulations to all the athletes who are competing in this year's Olympic Games!\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is my supreme honor to sing for you and cheer you on!\\\"\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She wrote.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel DMW's ex-wife, Sheila set to remarry, releases pre-wedding video  Celine Dion performs at 2024 Paris Olympics amid health battle [VIDEO]  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999865528583639, \"rank\": 8.82126076622893e-06, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2129, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"score\": 0.8401952147373124, \"rank\": 0.1844501759253757, \"text\": \"Sheila\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\"}, {\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7243965591357263e-36, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}]}"